0.1.0.name: wordpress/hundstall-404
0.1.0.description:
We love dogs. This plugin shows a random homeless dog on your 404. Why waste the space?

When installed, this WordPress plugin will override your theme’s 404 page and instead display a random homeless dog + links back to Hundstallet and to your homepage.

Since Hundstallet is a Swedish organization, all copy is in Swedish.
